abstract: TEN years after its premiere on CBS-TV, "And David Wept" re  ceived its first live staged performance Saturday night at the 92d Street Y, a production in this season's "Jewish Opera at the Y" series.

NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y., June 1  Beth Daniel, who is known on the Ladies' Professional Golf Association tour for exceptional distance off the tees and occasional displays of temper, won the Golden Lights Classic at the Wykagyl Country Club today as she beat Jo Ann Washam and Nancy LopezMelton by two strokes.

abstract: NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y., May 31-- Nancy Lopez-Melton, who shot the worst round of her professional golf career 14 days ago with an 83, shot her best round this season today with a sixunder-par 66 on the 6,410-yard Wykagyl Country Club course.
